Nollywood actor Uche Odoputa has raised alarm over the abduction of his father Kenneth Odoputa by kidnappers. The actor took to Instagram seeking support and prayers for the safe return of his dad who was abducted two weeks ago. Alongside a photo of his father, he wrote: “Friends please join me in praying for my father’s safe return from the hands of kidnappers that took him for over two weeks now Mr Kenneth Odoputa.” Celebrities sympathised with the actor in the comment section as they prayed for his father’s safe return. “The Lord will bring him back safe and grant you and your family strength in these trying times,” Chidi Mokeme wrote. Filmmaker Afam Okereke wrote: “God this is an experience I can’t wish even my enemy. May the good Lord take control, keep him safe and return him to us.”